#!/bin/sh
# Guard: refuse to push if the committed sample-report.pdf prints a version
# other than index.html's BC_CONFIG.version. Regenerate with:
#   node tools/gen-sample-report.mjs   (see DEPLOY.md)
#
# Enable this hook once per clone:  git config core.hooksPath tools/hooks
ROOT="$(git rev-parse --show-toplevel)"
CHECK="$ROOT/tools/hooks/check-sample-version.mjs"

if ! command -v node >/dev/null 2>&1; then
  echo "pre-push: node not found — skipping sample-report version check." >&2
  exit 0
fi
if [ ! -f "$CHECK" ]; then
  echo "pre-push: $CHECK missing — skipping sample-report version check." >&2
  exit 0
fi
node "$CHECK" || exit 1
exit 0
